name: Beirut August 4th 2020
description: A 2d animation NFT representing a particle simulation, that connotes the spread outwards of said particles, and then immediate regroupment. symbolizing the NFT's main concept "We are stronger together" - These particles represent the Lebanese people's first response to the incident.... This rare NFT is an edition of 207, same amount of the victims... Let this NFT bring back hope to the ones who have been directly targeted by this disaster.
